
Installation directions for ijkmcube.

Requires library expat available from expat.sourceforge.net.
Requires library ITKNrrdIO available from teem.sourceforge.net.

Install using cmake.
Type "ccmake ." and "c" twice to configure.
Check that IJK_DIR is set to the main ijk directory.
(If not, modify the path for IJK_DIR.)
Check that IJK_ISOTABLE_DIR is set to directory containing the
isosurface lookup tables.
(If not, modify the path for IJK_ISOTABLE_DIR.)
Press "g" to generate the Makefile and exit.
Type "cmake .".
Type "make" to create executables.
Type "make install" to install executables in ${IJK_DIR}/bin.

